Portions of the TradingView WebSocket protocol implementation in this
package (message framing, payload encoding, candle parsing, and
resolution mapping) are derived from gopher-lab/tradingview-go
(https://github.com/gopher-lab/tradingview-go), which is also released
under the MIT license. The original implementation is the source of
record for protocol-level details that are not officially documented by
TradingView.
